@neolit123 this change should not affect CSR code.

However, being the CSR thing built "improperly" on top of phases and the init workflow, there is a high risk that a change on one will impact the other.

My personal opinion is that in the long term CSR should be moved away because they are not part of the kubeadm init workflow

